OL,4,CGreen Homes Grant scheme to insulate
OL,5,Chouses axed
OL,6, A much-promoted grants programme to
OL,7, help UK householders insulate their
OL,8, homes is to be scrapped within days.
OL,10,FThe Green Homes Grant (GHG) reached
OL,11,Fjust 10% of the 600,000 homes the
OL,12,Fchancellor promised would be improved.
OL,14,FThe scheme will be stopped on Wednesday
OL,15,Fand the cash allocated to a separate
OL,16,Finsulation fund run by councils.
OL,18,FThe #300m previously allocated for the
OL,19,FGHG will now go into a programme
OL,20,Fadministered by local authorities,
OL,21,Ftargeted at lower income households.
